=== 目的 ===
This template enables the citation of articles from the Wikisource project [[s:en:1911 Encyclopædia Britannica|1911 Encyclopædia Britannica]] in the manner of {{tl|cite encyclopaedia}}.

=== 用法 ===
<code><nowiki>{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|英文版維基文庫名稱|註釋}}</nowiki></code>

此外，亦可加上<tt>author</tt>（作者）選項：

<code><nowiki>{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|author=作者名|英文版維基文庫名稱|註釋}}</nowiki></code>

=== 範例 ===
<code><nowiki>{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|Sigel, Franz}}</nowiki></code>

displays as:

{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|Sigel, Franz}}

and

<code><nowiki>{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|Sigel, Franz|A popular general of the American Civil War.}}</nowiki></code>

displays as:

{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|Sigel, Franz|A popular general of the American Civil War.}}

If the EB1911 article name is the same as the Wikipedia article name, and there is no optional comment, the template argument can be omitted.  For example, in the [[Uitenhage]] article

<code><nowiki>{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation}}</nowiki></code>

displays as:

{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|Uitenhage}}

Example using the <code>author</code> parameter:

<code><nowiki>{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|author=Ugo Balzani|Villani, Giovanni}}</nowiki></code>

displays as:

{{Wikisource1911Enc Citation|author=Ugo Balzani|Villani, Giovanni}}

